291
00:15:58,850 --> 00:16:01,975
School gives you various experiences.

292
00:16:04,025 --> 00:16:06,975
It may not be a problem now,

293
00:16:06,975 --> 00:16:09,525
but later on, it could become one.

294
00:16:10,350 --> 00:16:12,300
I wish

295
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:14,975
you would change your mind.

296
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:17,825
Before it's too late.

297
00:16:45,625 --> 00:16:47,375
Can we talk?

298
00:16:57,750 --> 00:16:59,500
You're still up?

299
00:16:59,825 --> 00:17:01,850
I'm not sleepy at all.

300
00:17:02,950 --> 00:17:05,900
It's like I'm waiting for my scores after a test.

301
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:09,200
What happened?
What did your parents say?

302
00:17:10,850 --> 00:17:13,500
I bet there was a debate after I left.

303
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:15,100
Be honest with me.

304
00:17:15,100 --> 00:17:17,100
What score did I get?

305
00:17:17,100 --> 00:17:19,350
