306
00:17:20,950 --> 00:17:22,250
I flunked?

307
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:25,675
I didn't pass?

308
00:17:25,675 --> 00:17:29,650
We have to break up now?

309
00:17:30,625 --> 00:17:32,375
Well...

310
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:35,025
Be honest with me.

311
00:17:35,025 --> 00:17:36,325
Is that it?

312
00:17:37,150 --> 00:17:38,625
No.

313
00:17:38,625 --> 00:17:41,925
I was just kidding.

314
00:17:41,925 --> 00:17:43,850
Passed!

315
00:17:43,850 --> 00:17:45,225
You passed.

316
00:17:45,225 --> 00:17:46,550
Really?

317
00:17:46,550 --> 00:17:48,225
I really passed?

318
00:17:50,850 --> 00:17:51,850
Really?

319
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:56,700
I passed!

320
00:17:58,975 --> 00:18:00,850
Aunt!

321
00:18:03,075 --> 00:18:04,450
Aunt!

322
00:18:05,925 --> 00:18:08,750
She said I passed.

323
00:18:08,750 --> 00:18:09,950
Really?

324
00:18:09,950 --> 00:18:12,425
Can you whip something up?
Let's celebrate.

325
00:18:14,525 --> 00:18:17,950
Why did you wake me up?

326
00:18:17,950 --> 00:18:19,200
Have a seat, Daese.

327
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:21,375
Sangnam has something to tell you.

328
00:18:21,375 --> 00:18:23,375
Okay. Go ahead.

329
00:18:25,025 --> 00:18:27,225
Congratulations, father.

330
00:18:27,225 --> 00:18:29,600
You're getting a daughter in law.

331
00:18:30,400 --> 00:18:31,350
What?

332
00:18:31,350 --> 00:18:32,900
You're awake now, aren't you?

333
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:34,150
I am!

334
00:18:34,150 --> 00:18:36,675
Who is it? Bring her right now! Right now!

335
00:18:36,675 --> 00:18:38,675
Wait until tomorrow.

336
00:18:39,150 --> 00:18:41,325
I actually met her.

337
00:18:41,325 --> 00:18:43,500
What? Without tell me?

338
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:45,175
It was like a pre-interview.

339
00:18:45,175 --> 00:18:48,475
They do that before the main interview.

340
00:18:48,475 --> 00:18:50,600
So? How was she?

341
00:18:50,600 --> 00:18:52,375
She's perfect for Sangnam.

342
00:18:53,050 --> 00:18:56,400
Sangnam told her he's poor, he dropped out

343
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:58,950
